或不誠實意圖而取用電腦》（針對任何帶有能夠犯法的意圖的網上言論，無需任何有關的犯法行為存在）<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"b520edbd73da53c2c9e74be771cb43829f38c757","tid":182751,"uid":71725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T09:48:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0004d5786f64a13729f036293a73f943661a03ac","tid":182751,"uid":63468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T09:51:24.000Z","msg":"不過算啦，連登仔不嬲都口一套做就另一套，個個都講反網23條，身體卻很誠實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d3256c2c37d928eeeb5eb22456789db9ced759","tid":182751,"uid":72475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T09:51:56.000Z","msg":"垃圾樓主幾時死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}